:

1. *Nestala* je bez traga. (She vanished without a trace.)
2. Tvrdili su da je *nestala* bez traga. (They claimed that she had vanished without a trace.)
3. Ona je *nestala* u dalekom gradu. (She disappeared in a distant city.)
4. *Nestala* je pre nego što je uspela da se obrati ljudima. (She disappeared before she was able to address people.)
5. Svi su čuli da je *nestal*. (Everyone heard that he had disappeared.)
6. *Nestale* su njene tragove. (Her traces have disappeared.)